    "en": {
      "title": "2 players of the Sri Lankan team are infected with Corona",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "All-rounder Dhananjaya de Silva and spinner Geoffrey Wendersay have been affected by the Covid-19 infection.",
        "According to Sri Lanka Cricket, both of them will not participate in the second Test match against Australia which starts tomorrow in Galle.",
        "It is reported that spinners Prabhat Jayasuriya and Lakshan Chandaken have been called into the squad for those players.",
        "During the rabbit antigen test conducted yesterday, the said players were found to be infected with Covid. (a)"
      ],
